            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have started to soften, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your<strong> orzo</strong> and <strong>pesto stock </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook, covered, for an initial 8-10 min</p><p>Tip: Stir the orzo occasionally to prevent it from sticking!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
