        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Drain your <strong>king prawns</strong></p><p>Once the orzo has had an initial 8-10 min, add the <strong>king prawns</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min further or until the prawns are cooked through and the orzo is tender</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
