    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the prawns are cooked through, add the <strong>grated cheese</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Season with <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> king prawn, pepper & pesto orzo</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash more water if your pan's looking a little dry!</p>",
